{"tid":2426531,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"亞視執董：亞視有意直播「林鍾大戰」","createTime":"2021-02-28T07:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T07:37:31.000Z","uid":368777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9634d8f9e847ec2aadae6a8bdcab2c8976392a6f","tid":2426531,"uid":368777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:03:05.000Z","msg":"-<br />\n<br />\n日前亞視執行董事陳偉傑出席《百萬拳王》大埔舉行記者會，陳偉傑主動提到近日林作與鍾培生的牙骹戰，更表示：「如果林作同鍾培生唔介意我哋幫佢搞直播，播埋佢哋嗰場拳賽都OK嘅。」他又講到暫時未有人聯絡自己，陳偉傑也會嘗試接洽林作和鍾培生。 <br />\n<br />\n被問到為何對這場拳賽有興趣，陳偉傑就指因為他們都需要場地，提到：「亞視係一個開放平台，我係可以贊助個擂台同搞直播啫，唔係抽佢水唔收佢錢嘅。」但《百萬拳王》節目負責人黎文狄就唔係咁睇，笑言：「我哋係驚佢打唔成啫。」似乎跟大家一樣，怕他們吹水做新聞多過真打，真係「唔怕你真打，最怕你縮沙。」<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.nmplus.hk/%e7%86%b1%e8%a9%b1/%e9%8d%be%e5%9f%b9%e7%94%9f%e6%9e%97%e4%bd%9c-%e4%ba%9e%e8%a6%96-%e7%9b%b4%e6%92%ad-ctb10-770903/4/</code></pre>"},{"pid":"440d92daf881f0b5e650fb2ab8a4b64059051ed3","tid":2426531,"uid":55386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:06:08.000Z","msg":"原來林生鍾生搞咁多野係幫亞記宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b6c93b04cb0bc3d6a1c7549467d79eb2fbf860","tid":2426531,"uid":368777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:06:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VmaKuYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmaKuYs.jpg&h=69781f9d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cef68b5d41a3aa37e5f0a150ad000bbe96feedc7","tid":2426531,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:08:35.000Z","msg":"鐘生收購亞視算啦"},{"pid":"4bef54903ebc99f41e82d8635c81c640c0bb1091","tid":2426531,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:11:25.000Z","msg":"歡樂今晚之歡天喜地擂台夜"},{"pid":"33e92ec0158f69cd8f85ef1fa5a00487a935dbda","tid":2426531,"uid":368777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cef68b5d41a3aa37e5f0a150ad000bbe96feedc7","tid":2426531,"uid":23445,"like